snippet.title: City destroying game Picokaiju by @spoike
snippet.description: Gameplay video on the latest update on 31st December 2021. In this PICO-8 roguelike you control a kaiju/move monster who wants to crush a hapless procedurally generated city. Available at https://spoike.itch.io/picokaiju and in Pico-8 BBS.
